i learned today is to not eat a potato raw.
A majority of the danger in any potato (but raw moreso) comes from the fact that potatos are a form of nightshade.
A majority of the toxins are in the skin though.
So skinned potatos are far less dangerous.
Though worst case scenario, even fully raw green potatos are really only going to cause an upset stomach. Might put you in the bathroom for a while.
